name: Vessels 155: SECURITY CHIEF XO
description: As well as being the crew’s Security Chief, the XO considers herself the team’s unofficial agony aunt and shoulder to cry on. If you look at her wrong, she will subject you to agonies the likes of which you could not conceive in your worst nightmares, and if you venture too close to her, she will impale your head on her spiked shoulder armour. A move certain to bring tears to your eyes! Or instant death, depending on where the spikes penetrate your skull.
